name: Another “World’s Largest” photo: See Tokyo like never before.
caption: 360gigapixels.com
description: Insanely gigantic photo from Tokyo’s tallest building. 360° degrees of incredible resolution. Shot in September 2012, this is an extremely finely detailed photo made from 8000 individual pictures. Can you find the gorilla wearing the ballet dress?
